Radamel Falcao, Arda Turan, Antoine Griezmann, Lucas Hernandez, Rodrigo and Thomas Partey are among others to be sold on at huge profits."In a war, those that win are not those with most soldiers, but those that use them best," Simeone once said in comparing how his side punch above their weight.Everyone is now aware that drawing Atletico in a Champions League knockout tie means a battle. And that is just how Simeone likes it.